<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62d1e026-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s4194"><num value="4194">§ 4194.</num><heading> Training and information</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary, in cooperation with eligible public entities, shall carry out training and information activities with respect to the guarantee program under this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62d1e027-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/330/tVI/s604">Pub. L. 104–330, title VI, § 604</ref>, <date date="1996-10-26">Oct. 26, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/4047">110 Stat. 4047</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
